data.description: This home is nestled in the pines in the very desirable Kingswood Estates. Great curb appeal with a paver driveway, wood and stone exterior and large wood columns supporting the front porch. Once inside, enjoy the open floor plan with a river rock gas fireplace, wood planked vaulted ceilings and plenty of windows to let in the Arizona sunshine and breathtaking pines. Plantation shutters are in the Livingroom, Formal Dining Room, Breakfast Nook and two of the five bedrooms. The kitchen has granite countertops, new stainless-steel Oven, Dishwasher and Refrigerator. Custom Oak cabinetry with under the counter lighting. Main Level living with the Master, one guest bedroom and laundry on the main floor. Enter the Master through French Doors, to a large room with a gas fireplace.
